text: Radio Tele La Brise is an educational, cultural, sports, and music Haitian radio and television station based in Camp-Perrin, Haiti. It is licensed by the Conatel of Haiti since July 23rd, 2010 ==See also== * Media of Haiti * Camp-Perrin ==References== ==External links== * Listen Online on ZenoLive * Watch Online on our website Category:Radio stations in Haiti
